{"tid":218539,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"庵野秀明《真・EVA劇場版》官方表示第4部正銳意製作中","createTime":"2017-04-26T14:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T05:27:54.000Z","uid":8565,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5e1555c243410398877fa34240da946543b7e2","tid":218539,"uid":8565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"推出間隔越來越大<br />\n從第3部《福音戰士新劇場版：Q》在2012年11月17日上映後，迄今已經快4年半了&hellip;&hellip;遲遲未見任何消息（除了今年2月在頒獎典禮上被東寶製片人爆料正在進行下一部作品，不過也沒明講是EVA）。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"http://evangelionlike.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevangelionlike.jp&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=da3c5bc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">evangelionlike.jp</a><br />\n每次媒體詢問起這個問題，庵野永遠都是說「會努力，請大家好好期待」之類的，加上Ｑ劇情各種超乎想像的展開，│▌作為備受矚目的系列最終作，卻一直不見消息&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32v13V4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32v13V4.jpg&h=44b4615b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2014到2016年間，Khara總共招募了3批新成員，在招募廣告上都註明了會參與EVA新劇場版的製作，也算是準備就緒，4月5日終於在官推曬出第4部劇場版的會議照片，並註明正在銳意製作中，難道庵野監督會在新劇場版系列10週年徹底填坑嗎？"},{"pid":"4d19f985a621ec936f2cfc72fe53dcdf95f01389","tid":218539,"uid":8565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1488042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1488042&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=64ac9289\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1488042</a>"},{"pid":"40f9c99d9585ca650420f0b7a9169243fb07514c","tid":218539,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"真&bull;新劇場版<br />\n又loop多十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8787d8fc70e4dec6003aa1631c624086fff96cb9","tid":218539,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"應該係真 哥斯奶第二集"},{"pid":"200d8